code: @Override public QueryBuilder asBuilder() {     return termQuery(term, value). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(term, value). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (this == obj) {         return true.     }     if (obj == null || getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     TermQuery other = (TermQuery) obj.     return Objects.equals(term, other.term) && Objects.equals(value, other.value). }
@Override protected String innerToString() {     return term + ":" + value. }
